              <div style="font-size: 40px; font-weight: 700; color: #FD1875; margin-bottom: 8px;">1</div>
              <h5 style="margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 14px; color: #e0e0e0;">Import or Pick Template</h5>
              <p class="sit-text-secondary" style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5;">Bring in an existing dashboard or start from one of 7 templates.</p>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center; padding: 16px;">
              <div style="font-size: 40px; font-weight: 700; color: #17A2B8; margin-bottom: 8px;">2</div>
              <h5 style="margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 14px; color: #e0e0e0;">Pick Theme + Effects</h5>
              <p class="sit-text-secondary" style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5;">12 themes, 13 backgrounds, 11 animations and 13 interactive controls.</p>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center; padding: 16px;">
              <div style="font-size: 40px; font-weight: 700; color: #5CC05C; margin-bottom: 8px;">3</div>
              <h5 style="margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 14px; color: #e0e0e0;">Preview + Polish</h5>
              <p class="sit-text-secondary" style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5;">See changes live. Add widgets like clocks, gauges, countdowns, QR codes.</p>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center; padding: 16px;">
              <div style="font-size: 40px; font-weight: 700; color: #F7B500; margin-bottom: 8px;">4</div>
              <h5 style="margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 14px; color: #e0e0e0;">Save or Download</h5>
              <p class="sit-text-secondary" style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5;">Save directly (on-prem) or Download XML and paste into Splunk Cloud.</p>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </html>
    </panel>
  </row>

  <!-- IMPORTANT NOTE -->
  <row>
    <panel>
      <html>
