              <p class="sit-text-secondary" style="margin: 4px 0 0; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5;">
                This toolkit targets Splunk's Classic Simple XML. It is <strong>not compatible with Dashboard Studio</strong>.
                Splunk Cloud users: use Download XML, then paste into a Classic dashboard via Source Editor.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </html>
    </panel>
  </row>

  <!-- FEATURES -->
  <row>
    <panel>
      <title>What's in the Toolkit</title>
