                <p class="sit-text-secondary" style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5;">Matrix data rain, particle networks, aurora borealis, cyberpunk grid pulse, radar sweep, starfield parallax.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sit-card">
              <div class="sit-card-body" style="padding: 16px;">
                <h4 style="color: #5CC05C; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 14px;">&#9881; 12 Interactive Controls</h4>
                <p class="sit-text-secondary" style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5;">Dark/light mode toggle, fullscreen, collapsible panels, auto-refresh countdown, keyboard shortcuts.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sit-card">
              <div class="sit-card-body" style="padding: 16px;">
                <h4 style="color: #8b5cf6; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 14px;">&#128203; HTML Widgets</h4>
                <p class="sit-text-secondary" style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5;">Live clocks, countdown timers, gauges, traffic lights, QR codes, team boards, weather, KPI progress rings.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sit-card">
              <div class="sit-card-body" style="padding: 16px;">
                <h4 style="color: #F7B500; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 14px;">&#10024; 29 Effects</h4>
                <p class="sit-text-secondary" style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5;">Panel hover glow, scroll reveal, typewriter text, number morph, stagger entrance, button ripples.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sit-card">
              <div class="sit-card-body" style="padding: 16px;">
                <h4 style="color: #e8a040; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 14px;">&#128274; Splunk Cloud Ready</h4>
                <p class="sit-text-secondary" style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5;">Cloud Mode downloads portable XML you paste via Source Editor. No REST API writes required.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </html>
    </panel>
  </row>

